OLD TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_DESC:0 "The §SDiplomacy§! screen is where we communicate with other civilizations. Here we can §SDeclare War§!, form §SAlliances§! and implement §STrade Deals§! with our neighbors, amongst other things."
NEW TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_DESC:1 "The §SDiplomacy§! screen is where we communicate with other civilizations. Here we can §SDeclare War§!, form §SAlliances§! and implement §STrade Deals§! with our neighbors, amongst other things.\n\nYour §SRelation§! with the selected Empire is shown as one of five levels, from Terrible to Excellent. In order to make a deal or agreement you must have a sufficent Relations level.\n\nYour §SEnvoys§! can be assigned to an Empire to bypass Relations requirements or to Improve or Harm Relations."
CN TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_DESC:1 "在§S外交§!界面，我们可以与其他文明开展交流。在这里，可以向邻国§S宣战§!，组建§S同盟§!以及制定§S贸易协定§!等等。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_DESC:1 "在§S外交§!界面，我们可以与其他文明进行交流。例如§S宣战§!、组建§S联盟§!、制定§S贸易协定§!等等。\n\n你与其他国家的§S关系§!将以五个级别显示出来，从恶劣到极佳。为了达成交易或者协议，必须拥有足够的关系级别。\n\n你的§S特使§!可以被指派去其他国家以绕开需求的关系等级或去改善、损害你们的关系。"
ADD TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_TRADE_TITLE:0 "Trade"
CN2 TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_TRADE_TITLE:0 "贸易"
ADD TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_TRADE_DESC:0 "This is the §STrade screen§!. We can trade any type of §SResource§! with an Empire, as well §SInformation§! and §SFavors§!.\n\nFavors can be spent to increase an Empire's willingness to accept an agreement. You can also call in Favors during a Vote on the Senate Floor in the Galactic Community to Boost your Diplomatic Weight."
CN2 TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_TRADE_DESC:0 "这是§S贸易界面§!。我们可以与其他国家交易任意一种类型的§S资源§!，也可以是§S情报§!和§S外交支持§!。\n\n外交支持可以增强另一个国家在接受协议时的意愿程度。你同样可以在星海共同体的参议院投票期间请求外交支持来增加你的外交权重。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_TRADE_DESC:0 "这是§S贸易界面§!。我们可以与其他国家交易任意一种类型的§S资源§!，也可以是§S情报§!和§S外交支持§!。\n\n外交支持可以增强另一个国家在接受协议时的意愿程度。你同样可以在银河共同体的参议院投票期间请求外交支持来增加你的外交话语权。"
ADD TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_FEDERATION_TITLE:0 "Federation Types"
CN2 TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_FEDERATION_TITLE:0 "联邦类型"
ADD TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_FEDERATION_DESC:0 "§SFederation Types§! dictate what the focus of the Federation will be. Each Federation type has unique starting §SPerks and Laws§! and will §SUnlock§! more Perks as it gains XP."
CN2 TUTORIAL_DIPLOMACY_VIEW_FEDERATION_DESC:0 "§S联邦类型§!决定了联邦发展的侧重点。每个联邦类型都有着独特的初始§S天赋和法律§!并且将会在获得经验值后§S解锁§!更多。"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_TITLE:0 "Federation Overview"
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_TITLE:0 "联邦总览"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_DESC:0 "This is the §HFederation screen§!. Our Federation will grow stronger while members maintain good §SCohesion§!. When a new member joins our Federation, some Cohesion is lost. Assigning Envoys to the Federation will improve Cohesion.\n\nAs our Federation grows stronger we §SUnlock Perks§! that increase our mutual benefits."
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_DESC:0 "这是§H联邦界面§!。我们的联邦会在成员国保持良好§S团结度§!的情况下变得更为强大。新成员国加入我们的联邦时会损失一些团结度。向联邦指派特使会提升团结度。\n\n随着我们的联邦更为强大，我们也会不断§S解锁增益§!以使我们在更高水平上互利共赢。"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_ENVOYS_TITLE:0 "Federation Envoys"
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_ENVOYS_TITLE:0 "联邦特使"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_ENVOYS_DESC:0 "Adding §HEnvoys§! to our Federation will help improve §SCohesion§!. Keep in mind that you are limited with how many Enoys you have. Envoys that are assigned to Federations can later be re-assigned to other §SDiplomatic Actions§!."
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_ENVOYS_DESC:0 "向我们的联邦添派§H特使§!有助于提升§S团结度§!。要注意的是你拥有的特使数量是有限的。被指派到联邦的特使可以随后重新指派到其他§S外交行动§!。"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_MEMBERS_TITLE:0 "Federation Members"
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_MEMBERS_TITLE:0 "联邦成员国"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_MEMBERS_DESC:0 "This is the §HFederation Members§! screen. Here we can see how powerful our §SMembers§! are in various areas, how many §SEnvoys§! they are contributing, and which of their §SEthic§! are conflicting and contributing to a loss of §SCohesion§!."
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_MEMBERS_DESC:0 "这里是§H联邦成员国§!界面。在此我们可以看到我们的§S成员国§!在多领域的实力和它们各自指派了多少§S特使§!。这里也会显示§S思潮§!间的冲突，这会导致§S团结度§!损失。"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_NAVY_TITLE:0 "Federation Navy"
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_NAVY_TITLE:0 "联邦海军"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_NAVY_DESC:0 "The §HFederation Navy§! is built from §SNavy Capacity§! given up by all Members, and is controlled by the §SPresident§!. Members can all build Federation Navy ships to contribute to the Fleet."
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_NAVY_DESC:0 "§H联邦海军§!的建造依赖于各成员国放弃的§S海军容量§!，并听命于§S主席国§!。成员国均可建造联邦海军舰船，为联邦舰队做贡献。"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_LAWS_TITLE:0 "Federation Laws"
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_LAWS_TITLE:0 "联邦法律"
ADD TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_LAWS_DESC:0 "Changes to §HFederation Laws§! can be proposed by any member. If the Federation fails to pass a Law, the Federation will suffer a §SCohesion Penality§!.\n\nSome Laws are Locked and require increasing the §SCentralization§! to unlock them. The Federation must first §SLevel Up§! to gain access to a Higher Centralization.\n\nBe cautious though, as the Centralization is increased, Cohesion will suffer."
CN2 TUTORIAL_FEDERATION_VIEW_LAWS_DESC:0 "任意成员国均可提议对§H联邦法律§!进行变更。如果联邦未能通过一条法律，则联邦会受到§S团结度惩罚§!。\n\n某些法律默认锁定，必须提升§S集权程度§!方能解锁。联邦必须先§S升级§!才能加强集权程度。\n\n注意，随着集权程度的加强，团结度将会受损。"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_TITLE:0 "The Galactic Community"
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_TITLE:0 "星海共同体"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_TITLE:0 "银河共同体"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_DESC:0 "Welcome to the §HGalactic Community§!, where Diplomats from around the Galaxy meet to decide Galactic Law by Voting on §SResolutions§!. You can support §SProposed Resolutions§! from the §SQueue§!, which will add your §SDiplomatic Weight§! to its total support. The Resolution with the most support in the Queue will move onto the §SSenate Floor§! once it is in Session. There it will be voted on whether it should become §SGalactic Law§!.\n\nTake note of the §SGalactic Focus§!, as it gives direction to a common goal for the Community.\n\nLastly you can see who all are members as well as any §SGalactic Modifiers§! that may be in play from Resolutions on this Screen."
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_DESC:0 "欢迎来到§H星海共同体§!，来自全星系的外交官在这里集会，以对§S议案§!投票的方式决定星系法。你可以支持§S队列§!中的一项§S已提出议案§!，这会为其增加等同于你的§S外交权重§!的支持度。队列中有着最高支持度的决议将在会期被提交给§S参议院§!。随后参议院会进行投票，决定其是否能成为§S星系法§!。\n\n要注意§S星系焦点§!，它会为社群的共同目标指明方向。\n\n最后，你可以这一界面看到所有成员国和可能因决议生效的所有§S星系修正§!。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_DESC:0 "欢迎来到§H银河共同体§!，来自全银河的外交官在这里集会，以对§S议案§!投票的方式决定银河法。你可以支持§S队列§!中的一项§S已提出议案§!，这会为其增加等同于你的§S外交权话语权§!的支持度。队列中有着最高支持度的决议将在会期被提交给§S参议院§!。随后参议院会进行投票，决定其是否能成为§S银河法§!。\n\n要注意§S银河焦点§!，它会为社群的共同目标指明方向。\n\n最后，你可以这一界面看到所有成员国和可能因决议生效的所有§S银河修正§!。"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_ENVOYS_TITLE:0 "Envoys"
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_ENVOYS_TITLE:0 "特使"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_ENVOYS_DESC:0 "§HEnvoys§! can be assigned to the Galactic Community to increase your §SDiplomatic Weight§!. Envoys that are assigned to the Galactic Community can later be re-assigned to other §SDiplomatic Actions§!."
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_ENVOYS_DESC:0 "§H特使§!可以被指派到星海共同体来提升你的§S外交权重§!。指派到星海共同体的特使随后也可以被重新指派到其他§S外交行动§!。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_ENVOYS_DESC:0 "§H特使§!可以被指派到银河共同体来提升你的§S外交话语权§!。指派到银河共同体的特使随后也可以被重新指派到其他§S外交行动§!。"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_SENATE_TITLE:0 "The Senate Floor"
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_SENATE_TITLE:0 "参议院"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_SENATE_DESC:0 "The §HSenate Floor§! is where the Galactic Community votes to Pass or Defeat the Resolution from the Queue which had the most support. As a member you can vote: §SYes, No, or Abstain§!. If the Resolution Passes it will become §SGalactic Law§!.\n\nEmpires who don’t Abstain will gain an §SOpinion Increase§! with Empires that voted on their side and a Decrease with those who voted against them.\n\nIf you have gained diplomatic §SFavors§! from other Empires, you may use them here to boost your Diplomatic Weight on the Sentate Floor vote."
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_SENATE_DESC:0 "§H参议院§!是星海共同体决定队列中最高支持度的议案能否通过的场所。作为成员国，你可以投：§S赞成票，反对票或弃权票§!。如果决议通过，其将成为§S星系法§!。\n\n没有投弃权票的帝国将会§S提升§!那些与其投票相同的帝国的评价，降低与之投票相反的帝国的评价。\n\n如果你从其他帝国获得了§S外交支持§!，你可以在此使用它们来增加你在参议院投票中的外交权重。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_SENATE_DESC:0 "§H参议院§!是银河共同体决定队列中最高支持度的议案能否通过的场所。作为成员国，你可以投：§S赞成票，反对票或弃权票§!。如果决议通过，其将成为§S银河法§!。\n\n没有投弃权票的帝国将会§S提升§!那些与其投票相同的帝国的评价，降低与之投票相反的帝国的评价。\n\n如果你从其他帝国获得了§S外交支持§!，你可以在此使用它们来增加你在参议院投票中的外交话语权。"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_RESOLUTIONS_TITLE:0 "Resolutions"
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_RESOLUTIONS_TITLE:0 "议案"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_RESOLUTIONS_DESC:0 "The §HResolutions§! screen is a list of the currently enacted resolutions. You may §SPropose a New Resolution§! by selecting it from a Resolution chain, which will cost you Influence.\n\nYou may only propose the first un-enacted Resolution in the chain, you must lay the groundwork before proposing more radical changes, and even then not everyone will support them.\n\nIf a Resolution passes, the next Resolution in the chain can not be proposed for many years."
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_RESOLUTIONS_DESC:0 "§H议案§!界面显示了目前生效的议案列表。你可以从议案链中选择并§S提议一项新议案§!，这会消耗影响力。\n\n你只可提出议案链中第一项未生效的议案，在进行激进的改革前必须先打下基础，即使如此也不是每个人都会支持。\n\n如果议案通过，议案链中的下一项议案在很长一段时间内将无法被提议。"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_COUNCIL_TITLE:0 "The Galactic Council"
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_COUNCIL_TITLE:0 "星系理事会"
ADD TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_COUNCIL_DESC:0 "The §HGalactic Council§! has been established. An §SElection§! will begin, and the members with the most diplomatic weight will gain §SCouncil Positions§!. Council members have an increased Diplomatic Weight and can push a Proposal to the Senate Floor as an §SEmergency Resolution§!.\n\nThe §SCouncil Veto§! ability can be unlocked by passing resolutions to strengthen the Council. Council members also have access to §SSpecial Resolutions§!."
CN2 TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_COUNCIL_DESC:0 "§H星系理事会§!已经成立。一场§S选举§!将会开始，拥有最高外交权重的各成员国将得到§S议会席位§!。议会成员国的外交权重将会提高，并可以以§S紧急决议§!的形式直接向参议院提交提议。\n\n§S议会否决权§!可以在通过加强议会的决议后解锁。议会成员也可以使用§S特殊决议§!。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_COUNCIL_DESC:0 "§H银河理事会§!已经成立。一场§S选举§!将会开始，拥有更高外交话语权的诸成员国将得到§S理事会席位§!。理事会成员的外交话语权将会提高，并可以以§S紧急议案§!的形式直接向参议院提交提议。\n\n§S理事会否决权§!可以依靠通过议案来解锁来加强理事会。理事会成员也可以使用§S特殊议案§!。"
ADD TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_TITLE:0 "Empire Sprawl"
CN2 TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_TITLE:0 "帝国规模"
ADD TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_DESC:0 "§HEmpire Sprawl§! is a measure of the territorial expanse of your empire in the form of controlled Systems, Colonies, Districts, and Total Population.\n\nA high Empire Sprawl is a strain on your empire's §SAdministrative Capacity§!, and will increase the cost of §STechnologies§!, §STraditions§!, §SLeaders§!, and §SEdicts§!"
CN2 TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_DESC:0 "§H帝国规模§!是量化衡量帝国所控制的领土，其依据包括控制的恒星系、殖民地、区划及总人口的多少。\n\n帝国规模过大会对帝国的§S行政管理能力§!形成压力，并将提高§S科技§!、§S传统§!、§S领袖§!以及§S法令§!的花费。"